title 0.6: new note spa

note left of browser:
user inputs text to form
and clicks Submit button
end note

note over browser:
browser executes the JS event handler
that handles the form submit event:

creates a new note,
adds it to the notes list,
rerenders the note list on the page,
and sends the new note to the server.
end note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa

server->browser: HTTP status code 201 (created)